data.description: Welcome Home! this is a  well maintained property! You have found a Gem.  A solid home under $150,000 in West Philadelphia.  This house has three bedrooms (only two bedrooms pictured) , a spacious basement and a back yard ready for entertaining guests.  The updated eat in  Kitchen is Huge. You still have a spacious dining room.  Your comfortable living room which has two entrances is there for your leisure too.  This home is ready for the next owner.  Although this property is being sold as-is, come visit home. All mortgage types are welcomed.
